# The Anarchist's Guide to Tech

The World Wide Web is the most successful anarchist project in human history.  To learn tech as an anarchist is to learn the ways of the web and to be able to control it and use it to your ends.

 - Learn hacker history and culture!
 - What is the World Wide Web?
 - What is the Internet?
 - What would the world look like without Big Tech?
 - Make your own web page!
 - Learn the languages of the web!
 - Learn the magic of P5!
 - Learn science in the web with Jupyter notebooks!
 - Build your own hardware with circuit python!
 - Build your own local web server 
